headline: Ulta Beauty Earnings Crush Estimates. The Stock Slumps.

headline: ULTA Q2 Deep Dive: Market Share Gains, New Brands, and International Expansion Drive Results
summary: Beauty, cosmetics, and personal care retailer Ulta Beauty (NASDAQ:ULTA) reported Q2 CY2025 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 9.3% year on year to $2.79 billion. The company’s full-year revenue guidance of $12.05 billion at the midpoint came in 2.8% above analysts’ estimates. Its GAAP profit of $5.78 per share was 14.6% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
